{"tid":2152363,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"為C.朗分擔壓力！派路上任後首簽莫拉達","createTime":"2020-08-12T02:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T09:57:24.000Z","uid":25345,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"8fc7fa09351baf0f3db56d090b2a44fa200c1d94","tid":2152363,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2020/08/12/7/7f031afe5d353e403ec3a3179c186cdd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2020%2F08%2F12%2F7%2F7f031afe5d353e403ec3a3179c186cdd.jpg&h=917726e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  派路（Andrea Pirlo）出任祖雲達斯教練後，希望引進莫拉達（Alvaro Morata）加強鋒線。<br />\n<br />\n  《SportItalia》稱，派路打算對鋒線進行調整，希古恩（Gonzalo Higuain）預計會離隊，戴巴拿（Paulo Dybala）則會更多負責邊路，中路要有一人為C.朗拿度分擔壓力，祖記新帥的目光瞄向了莫拉達。2014-15賽季，派路和莫拉達同在祖雲達斯踢球，奪得國內雙冠王，並在歐聯攻入了決賽。<br />\n<br />\n  莫拉達今季在馬體會出場34次，攻入12球。他和家人很喜歡意大利的生活，在都靈有房產，並經常回去渡假。不過，馬體會預計會對這位27歲中鋒開出一筆較高要價，至少不會低於去年夏天引進他的6500萬歐元。"},{"pid":"eead2cd9ac03bc59e255491e162d43eb49f91d7a","tid":2152363,"uid":197015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce98e8ad0845b9fa6954fa5cc4ccb345b8ed6fd2","tid":2152363,"uid":25345,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T02:57:15.000Z","msg":"牙朗：屌你老母"},{"pid":"03bd1dbfa6f19d2ab0fae549abea04982031a0ae","tid":2152363,"uid":21842,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T03:01:19.000Z","msg":"會増加壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"642a284785dd9eb6fb82650c51efc9c38e83b2b6","tid":2152363,"uid":9256,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T03:01:23.000Z","msg":"呢條垃圾點解成日有大會想買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5